    "# 10 — Neural Operators for Cellular Simulation\n",
    "\n",
    "**Adaptive Multiscale Biological Simulation AI**\n",
    "\n",
    "Phase 4: Field-level simulation using Fourier Neural Operators (FNO).\n",
    "\n",
    "FNOs learn continuous operators mapping one field to another.\n",
    "Much faster than PDE solvers — pre-train once, then simulate in milliseconds.\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook covers:\n",
    "1. FNO architecture and spectral convolutions\n",
    "2. Cellular population dynamics\n",
    "3. Signaling field prediction\n",
    "4. Coarse-graining for biological systems\n",
    "5. Training pipeline for FNO models\n",
    "6. Comparison: FNO vs. traditional PDE solvers"
   ]
  },
